{"tid":2512071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求政府強制所有公務員打針","createTime":"2021-05-01T11:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T11:49:59.000Z","uid":310307,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f341288018acec8ca617e1a789013d706b355689","tid":2512071,"uid":310307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:46:32.000Z","msg":"政府呢一邊廂<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">強制</span></span>指定場所嘅員工同埋外傭打針 <br />\n但係另一邊廂就就咁<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">建議</span></span>公務員要打針 <br />\n屌你老母你有咩問題 <br />\n迫人打針已經唔啱 <br />\n屌你老母成班柒古碌公墓員點解可以唔洗強制打<br />\n你班柒古碌公墓員逗政府份糧逗得咁撚開心 <br />\n但係又唔洗打針？<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">要打都係你班柒古碌打先 </span></span><br />\n強烈建議全部公墓員打科興 打十針 <br />\n屌你老母班柒古碌<br />\n唔撚打就辭職 學聶德權話齋 <br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">佢哋可以選擇唔做政府</span></span></span><br />\n屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddccc87940786369478382ef111f96dd549fb7b","tid":2512071,"uid":310307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"217b37f8759bd84b053a1d4d02a96af21102fe32","tid":2512071,"uid":310307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"a87df16ed5f62592f883b244d588f6dbb62f2eb3","tid":2512071,"uid":310307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:48:02.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"5ccf762fdd1e63030514471d39e0110912ddcc34","tid":2512071,"uid":310307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"b14b2